---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="About Jerry Chen — computer science at McGill, working across SWE, AI, and NLP research."
>
  <h1 class="text-3xl">About</h1>

  <section class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-6 sm:flex-row sm:items-start sm:gap-8">
    <figure
      class="shrink-0 overflow-hidden border border-border bg-surface"
      style="width: 180px; aspect-ratio: 4 / 5;"
    >
      <img
        src="/images/jerry.jpg"
        alt="Jerry Chen"
        width="180"
        height="225"
        class="h-full w-full object-cover"
      />
    </figure>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      <p>
        I'm Jerry, a computer science student at McGill University. This site
        is where I keep track of what I'm building, reading, and thinking about
        — it started because I wanted a quieter place than LinkedIn to document
        the work.
      </p>
      <p>
        <em>Replace this paragraph with a more personal bio during the content
        seeding step.</em>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-12">
    <h2 class="font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted">
      What I work on
    </h2>
    <div class="mt-4 space-y-4">
      <p>
        My work spans three loose tracks. <strong>Software engineering</strong>{" "}
        — typical full-stack and systems projects, the kind of work you do to
        ship things that people actually use.{" "}
        <strong>AI development</strong> — building with LLMs and foundation
        models, applied rather than theoretical.{" "}
        <strong>NLP / LLM research</strong> — a more academic slice, closer to
        understanding how these models work than shipping features with them.
      </p>
      <p>
        Projects on this site are tagged
        <a href="/projects?tag=swe">SWE</a>,
        <a href="/projects?tag=ai">AI</a>, or
        <a href="/projects?tag=nlp">NLP</a> so you can filter to the track you
        care about.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mt-12">
    <h2 class="font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-muted">
      Elsewhere
    </h2>
    <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 font-sans text-sm">
      <li>
        <span class="text-muted">Email</span> ·{" "}
        <a href="mailto:jerry.chen@mail.mcgill.ca">jerry.chen@mail.mcgill.ca</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <span class="text-muted">GitHub</span> ·{" "}
        <a href="https://github.com/Lil-Chen05">github.com/Lil-Chen05</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-muted">
      Add LinkedIn or any other link during the content seeding step if you
      want it here.
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
